ion. <strong>Note that we do not construct our happiness measure in each country using these<br />\nsix factors &ndash; the scores are instead based on individuals&rsquo; own assessments of their lives, as indicated by the Cantril ladder.</strong> Rather, we use the six variables to explain the variation of happiness across countries."},{"pid":"943a4b58e57bce8c5f434acedd07f6a29c6d3df2","tid":1070970,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3274263acba37ada99c2c23c17e949a98ae5104e","tid":1070970,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"623cc5170c7bede6fcb4b19c55b6abd4ae7b449a","tid":1070970,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"855b9c55f5ba0e9c710576c4a1e7295b1aca7f72","tid":1070970,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"聯合國班撚屌都亂咁黎<br />\n東亞點會係繁體支那最幸福呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點計都應該係我地香港幸福no.1啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acyJTzV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacyJTzV.png&h=41f70b3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"我諗台北以外嘅人係真係幾幸福"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"其實都未必<br />\n台灣人視台北為搵錢地方<br />\n正如香港俾鬼佬視為搵錢地方一樣<br />\n世界上搵錢地方其實就=廝殺之地競爭激烈<br />\n但人地搵夠就返屋企<br />\n香港人一係移民一係就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"我諗台北以外部分台灣人對搵錢嘅 mindset 應該同香港人好唔同<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係佢地應該同香港人一樣唔開心"},{"pid":"a7d9100632da290526707ce0e6587a668bb3bf0a","tid":1070970,"uid":128761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"真係唔該你，咁就清晰好多<br />\n係最後一項香港真係低到冇問題<br />\n如果唔係香港真係應該頭10幾"},{"pid":"d98dfa03356e5e96ed6fd9270af4b92110c4f219","tid":1070970,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd06b5054a4